    "causal_summary": "`invalidateProviderSingleton()` (`shared/embeddings.ts`) nulls `providerInstance` without calling any dispose, so the outgoing `HfLocalProvider`'s native ONNX/ORT session (held transitively via `extractor.model.sessions[].handler`) is orphaned on every provider swap — the native memory the GC cannot reclaim and `--max-old-space-size` cannot bound (RC-1)",
